{"tid":339600,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[單春粉醒下啦] 已經對陳奕迅好陌生","createTime":"2017-07-29T08:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T14:38:08.000Z","uid":28802,"like":316,"dislike":100,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a638aa0bedf7765c042961ec1211d3f558ed1fa","tid":339600,"uid":28802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T08:03:51.000Z","msg":"單春喺我出世嗰年出道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n細個沙士帶緊口罩已經開始聽人來人往 明年今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚睇劇仲有歲月如歌聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上左初中，佢出U87 日日loop 阿牛 葡萄成熟時身邊嘅frd, 同學都好鍾意佢 loop loop 下自己都鍾意埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n高中一路溫書一路有 今天只要一件事 撐住，每次聽完都勁正面 比到好多正能量 MSN嘅status永遠都係你嘅歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中學畢業嗰年 同成班frd喺sing con 唱重口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾到好多回憶我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 畢業無耐仲同當時都鍾意單春嘅男朋友去左Eason's Life睇人生第一次紅館演唱會<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗰年暑假都仲有 任我行 失憶蝴蝶 喺電話嘅playlist徘徊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到書都讀完 出嚟做嘢 開始認真細味Wyman, 夕爺為你填詞嘅歌 不過聽到四季 對你嘅感覺好冷淡 瘡桑嘅聲線 連自己嘅歌嘅詞都喺頒獎禮度唱錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近日喺某蝗電視節目入面嘅你真係好陌生 <br />\n多謝你呢十幾年 唱過咁多膾炙人口嘅歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但往事只能回味 人會變 歌唔會<br />\n希望Eason嘅粉可以醒一醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">佢已經唔係以前果個陳奕迅喇</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/large/184f000353a2f0d1f477\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F184f000353a2f0d1f477&h=24